reviews.text: 南記燒鵝真係好好食👍👍👍必食👍👍👍
燒鵝飯非常美味👍

27 Jul 19: 雖然個個都話佢D燒鵝好食，但我仍然覺得深井好味D（唔好同中環一樂比較）。我地係隔離買海鮮$1700，6大4小，南記收$1300。侍應服務一般，碗碟污糟，唔洗過唔建議用，地下都唔係乾淨，小朋友坐嘅櫈安全帶已經爛晒，而且都係較舊。

粉絲蒸扇貝：我鍾意粉絲點豉油食，但哩間我覺得做唔到我平時食果個效果。

燒鵝：我覺得佢個皮係幾脆，但鵝肥膏太多。肉都唔夠嫩，食落都係要用牙力先扯得郁。鵝味唔夠，無深井燒鵝上枱已經聞到果種香。

十分繁忙的飯店,人流多
單多到漏單,追單也久等個半鐘
待應還說要叫起,樣樣都叫起
實在令人久等
服務態度極差

result.name: Seafood Thai

reviews.text: Seafood Thai is a good location to have your seafood cooked and served for you. Yes, that is is correct. At this restaurant you must come with your proteins and then select how you want it cooked or what you want as side dishes. When I arrived at this restaurant and informed that I had to purchase the fish from the local markets 3 minutes away (walking).  Once I arrived at the open markets, I selected some shrimp, oysters and a fish to be cooked. It was interesting to have my meal wiggling in a bag as I walked back and selected how they are to be seasoned and cooked. The menu has English notes so picking and showing the waiter was not difficult. I had the fish baked in a soy sauce, shells with a cheese and wine cream, then the shrimp baked with a zesty dry curry. After having a beer my meal came in stages. Each very delicious and  with a drastically different flavor. This restaurant was a little pricier when you typically pay due to the fact that you are making two purchases but it is well worth the cost. The food is fresh and you are selecting from a live menu. This would be a good place for a date or to bring your family. You can even bring in your own wine so you have plenty of options. If you are in Hong Kong and have some time, take a ride to Seafood Thai bring your fish of and wine of choice and enjoy some Thai rice with your custom meal.
Too strong and lost the taste of seafood should have. Some seafood are overcooked, what a waste!
Delicious and fresh seafood is served here.  One of the signature dishes is the buttery lobster, which you don't find anywhere else, or at least not as good as this!
Very nice food and price is reasonable
Wonderful sea food experience. You can find evey kind here. Food is delicious and not expensive.
